title.narrative: ENHANCED MULTI-SECTORAL COOPERATION

description.narrative: Strengthening risk communication and community engagement in COVID-19 response,which contributes to Child Protection # Strengthen Families And Communities, Children With Disabilities, Early Childhood Development, Health Systems Strengthening, Immunization, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children, Prevention Of Stunting And Other Forms Of Malnutrition, Sanitation, Sanitation (Covid). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Girls, boys and caregivers, especially those affected by poverty, adversity and exclusion progressively utilise quality, equitable, mutually reinforcing systems of health, social and child protection, including in situation of humanitarian crisis by 2021.
